description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a registered nurse looking for extra work to fit aroundother commitments? Then joining our Bank may be of interest to you. Weprovide specialist palliative care to the population of eastern Hertfordshire and we are seeking Staff Nurses who are available to work on a bank basis and who are passionate about providing high quality care to patients nearing the end of their lives. Our In Patient Unit issituated in Welwyn Garden City, close to the Urgent Care Centre. Shifts generally available are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Earlies - 7.30am to 3.30pm, Lates 2pm to 10pm, Nights 9.30pm to 8am including bank holidays and weekends. Rates of pay range from £13 per hour weekdays to £16.90 per hour Nights and Saturdays, £20.80 per hour Sundays and bank holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous palliative care experience or experience working in oncology or with terminally ill patients preferred but not essential, however you must be a Level 1 registered nurse keen to develop your skills in this area. Induction &amp; training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer free on site parking, free uniform, free tea and coffee and the opportunity to work as part of a small, dedicated team providing the best possible care to patients and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
